  "page": "Siege of Longtable",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">siege of Longtable</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Longtable\" title=\"Longtable\">Longtable</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\nThe <a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">greens</a> taking <a href=\"/index.php/Longtable\" title=\"Longtable\">Longtable</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\"><img alt=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/32px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/48px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/64px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">Blacks</a></b>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Merryweather\" title=\"House Merryweather\"><img alt=\"House Merryweather.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/House_Merryweather.svg/20px-House_Merryweather.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/House_Merryweather.svg/30px-House_Merryweather.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/House_Merryweather.svg/40px-House_Merryweather.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Merryweather\" title=\"House Merryweather\">House Merryweather</a></li></ul></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\"><img alt=\"Aegon II Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/32px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/48px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/64px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">Greens</a></b>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\"><img alt=\"House Hightower.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/20px-House_Hightower.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/30px-House_Hightower.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/40px-House_Hightower.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Merryweather\" title=\"House Merryweather\"><img alt=\"House Merryweather.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/House_Merryweather.svg/20px-House_Merryweather.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/House_Merryweather.svg/30px-House_Merryweather.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/House_Merryweather.svg/40px-House_Merryweather.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Merryweather\" title=\"Lady Merryweather\">Lady Merryweather</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\"><img alt=\"House Hightower.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/20px-House_Hightower.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/30px-House_Hightower.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/40px-House_Hightower.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Ormund_Hightower\" title=\"Ormund Hightower\">Ormund Hightower</a></td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>siege of Longtable</b> occurred during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Siege\">Siege</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Siege_of_Longtable&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Siege\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_on_the_Honeywine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battle on the Honeywine\">Battle on the Honeywine</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Ormund_Hightower\" title=\"Ormund Hightower\">Ormund Hightower</a> and Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_Targaryen_(son_of_Viserys_I)\" title=\"Daeron Targaryen (son of Viserys I)\">Daeron Targaryen</a> forced the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Oakheart\" title=\"House Oakheart\">Oakhearts</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rowan\" title=\"House Rowan\">Rowans</a>, and the lords of the <a href=\"/index.php/Shield_Islands\" title=\"Shield Islands\">Shield Islands</a> to submit to King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\">Aegon II Targaryen</a>. While Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a> took <a href=\"/index.php/Fall_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Fall of King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, Ormund marched on <a href=\"/index.php/Longtable\" title=\"Longtable\">Longtable</a>, seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Merryweather\" title=\"House Merryweather\">House Merryweather</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Ormund's siege of Longtable forced numerous refugees to flee before his host to <a href=\"/index.php/Bitterbridge\" title=\"Bitterbridge\">Bitterbridge</a>. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Thorne\" title=\"Rickard Thorne\">Rickard Thorne</a> tried to bring Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Maelor_Targaryen\" title=\"Maelor Targaryen\">Maelor Targaryen</a> and his <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon_egg\" title=\"Dragon egg\">dragon egg</a> to the safety of Ormund's camp outside Longtable, but the pair were killed at Bitterbridge. <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Caswell\" title=\"Lady Caswell\">Lady Caswell</a> sent Maelor's dragon egg to Ormund.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Merryweather\" title=\"Lady Merryweather\">Lady Merryweather</a> eventually yielded Longtable to Ormund, who claimed the castle's wealth and food but did no harm to the Merryweathers. Lord Hightower then marched on <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Bitterbridge\" title=\"Sack of Bitterbridge\">Bitterbridge</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/First_Battle_of_Tumbleton\" title=\"First Battle of Tumbleton\">Tumbleton</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Siege_of_Longtable&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Triumphant.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;colo